.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
City: berlin, london, miami, new-york, liverpool, boston, marseilles
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| City          | berlin | london | liverpool | new-york | boston | marseilles | miami |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

