.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, indie, jazz, metal, r&b, rock
There 7 different types of food: peach, plum, cranberry, lemon, zucchini, pumpkin, banana
 1. the fan of metal is the person eating plum##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the person eating peach is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the fan of indie is the person eating zucchini##1
10. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the fan of folk##1
11. the person eating banana is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | rock     | jazz     | indie      | folk | metal      | disco     |
| Food   | lemon | cranberry | pumpkin | zucchini | banana | plum | peach |

