 3. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the futuristic house##1
 8. the palace house is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| House   | colonial  | gothic-revival | tower | palace | ranch-style     | cape-cod | futuristic |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

