.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, ice-hockey, biathlon, climbing, weightlifting, golf
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, boat, jet-ski, subway, tram, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Sport        | tennis | surfing | ice-hockey | biathlon     | weightlifting | golf | climbing |
| Transport   | tram | jet-ski  | van    | airplane | subway | bike       | boat   |

