 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Food   | pumpkin    | orange    | kiwi   | strawberry | grapefruit | watermelon | potato   |
| Cigar    | swisher | prince | dunhill | bongani  | havana       | fonseca     | dannemann |

